/* 2000s */It originally said, for his role in The Patriot, that there were rumors Isaacs would be nominated for Best Supporting Actor at the 72nd Academy Awards. But it actually would have been the 73rd Academy Awards. The 72nd Academy Awards honored films released in the year 1999, whereas the 73rd Academy Award honored films released in the following year 2000, which was the year The Patriot was released.
